text: Leo McGuirk (3 May 1908 - 27 March 1973) was an Australian cricketer. He played one first-class match for New South Wales in 1930/31. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1908 births Category:1973 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers
